org.dkpro.statistics.agreement.coding

Class CodingAnnotationItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dkpro.statistics.agreement.coding.CodingAnnotationItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICodingAnnotationItem, IAnnotationItem

    public class CodingAnnotationItem
extends Object
implements ICodingAnnotationItem
    Default implementation of ICodingAnnotationItem holding the set of annotation units for this item (i.e., the categories assigned to this item by all raters). When using the default implementation, it is recommended to use CodingAnnotationStudy.addItem(Object...) instead of instantiating this type.
    Author:
    Christian M. Meyer
    See Also:
    CodingAnnotationStudy, ICodingAnnotationItem
